HOW TO APPLY THE Z1 FIX FOR OPENWSN
-----------------------------------
In order to properly upload OpenWSN code on the Zolertia Z1 mote, it is sufficient to run

$ ./applyFix.sh

It will copy the proper files in the in the firmware and software of OpenWSN.

WARNING
It assumes that the two folders "openwsn-fw" and "openwsn-sw" are in the same directory.


